<L>__{exterior tremont street financial district. day}
<A>__{detective 1 trails captain queenan through the crowds of people heading towards work.}
<L>__{interior park st. subway station. morning}
<A>__{queenan begins to light a cigarette and then gives it up. a train comes in, and queenan boards. detective 1 boards the next car.}
<L>__{interior detective 1's subway car. moments later}
<A>__{looking through smeared glass into the next car as the train begins to move detective 1 sees queenan answer a cell call.}
<L>__{interior queenan's subway car. continuous}
<A>__{queenan is on his cell.}
<C>__{queenan}
<D>__{where are you now?}
<C>__{billy}
<D>__{look down the car.}
<A>__{queenan looks up mildly as the car rocks.}
<C>__{billy }
<D>__{got me?}
<A>__{queenan's pov: billy is slumped in a seat at the far end, not looking towards queenan.}
<C>__{billy }
<D>__{any reason you'd have a tail?}
<C>__{queenan}
<D>__{no...of course not.}
<C>__{billy}
<P>__{(on the verge of hyperventilating)}
<D>__{i'm watching a guy...}
<C>__{queenan}
<D>__{i don't have a tail, billy.}
<A>__{through the glass we see detective 1 watching queenan.}
<C>__{billy}
<D>__{okay. get off at south station. you wait there for ten minutes. after i leave i will text message you the address where we'll meet. i will make sure you don't have a tail.}
<C>__{queenan}
<D>__{south station. wait ten minutes.}
<A>__{as the train stops billy vaults off of it. on the platform he walks along, texting.}
